comments: Alexander-Walker (MIN) extends his off-arm and initiates contact with White's (BOS) upper body that dislodges him from his legally obtained defensive position during the drive.
Horford (BOS) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Towns (MIN) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) establishes himself in Brown's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Holiday (BOS) is moving alongside Anderson's (MIN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Anderson (MIN) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before his shot attempt.
Holiday (BOS) retreats in Anderson's (MIN) path when incidental lower-body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Alexander-Walker (MIN) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Holiday (BOS) contests McDaniels's (MIN) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
McDaniels (MIN) shot does not make contact with the rim and goes out of bounds. BOS is correctly rewarded with possession of the ball.
Towns (MIN) is drawn into the air on the pump fake and as he lands he initiates contact to Tatum's (BOS) body, which affects the jump shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) briefly grasps Edwards' (MIN) arm before releasing as he defends Edwards' dribble on the perimeter. The contact is marginal.

Replay review of the foul called on White (BOS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. White does not maintain verticality as he turns his body and leans to the side when contact occurs with Edwards (MIN), which affects his driving shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) retreats in Tatum's (BOS) path when he slides his hand off Tatum, and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
McDaniels (MIN) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Reid (MIN) reaches in and initiates contact with Tatum's (BOS) right arm, which affects his SQBR during his dribble.
As Brown (BOS) gains possession of the rebound, Edwards (MIN) swipes down and makes incidental hand-on-ball contact with Brown.
Towns (MIN) steps forward and into Tatum's (BOS) path, initiating contact to Tatum's lower body, which affects his SQBR during the drive.
Towns (MIN) moves alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Reid (MIN) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Holiday's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Alexander-Walker (MIN) throws the ball off of White (BOS) who is out of bounds, making him last to touch it before the ball goes out of bounds. MIN correctly retains possession of the ball.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Brown (BOS) throws an errant pass, and Horford (BOS) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Edwards (MIN) lifts and replants his pivot foot prior to releasing the ball to dribble.
Brown (BOS) rests a hand on Edwards' (MIN) side and marginal contact occurs before he retracts it as Edwards enters his upward shooting motion.
Towns (MIN) dislodges the ball from Brown (BOS) and is last to make contact before it goes out of bounds.
Anderson (MIN) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Towns (MIN) overtly extends his leg and initiates contact to Brown's (BOS) lower body affecting his ability to contest the jump shot attempt.
